ote":{"pid":"25cf0104cad9d3473d8bd16da30a060511621daf","tid":2238681,"uid":29929,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:37:59.000Z","msg":"牛頓都先得50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁全球含得撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39d80e8faf9f723399f6c2a2b3d01739fab5e77","tid":2238681,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"強帖留名"},{"pid":"e71a7676a233ad81f79058c8735bc8425a74cc01","tid":2238681,"uid":38861,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c5fabe8627aef6c19dc4e56edef39b0640a30963","tid":2238681,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"根本RNA病毒就難有準確疫苗<br />\n如果有 傷風感冒菌一早絕種 愛滋病都絕種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"武肺病毒非常依賴自己表面的Spike protein入侵人體細胞，如果疫苗所產生的抗體能夠有效同S protein結合，因而阻止病毒的S protein與人體細胞的ACE2結合，係可以有阻擋功效。"},{"pid":"86e00e8d52dc9e1576dd4e3fbc302bb02f19807d","tid":2238681,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94ada84e444901ddc4e5977298622fce4d2e443f","tid":2238681,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"打左疫苗唔一定唔中<br />\n可以係中左但冇咁嚴重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"無錯，至少牛津疫苗係馬騮實驗中裡頭睇到，注射咗疫苗的馬騮感染武肺在頭三日都可以病毒依然應夠繁殖，只不過其後病毒數量會大幅減少同埋唔會出現嚴重武肺徵狀。"},{"pid":"2ac62a6eb61f6fb017f636ff5cc2f99b03a8a133","tid":2238681,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8cda8ac30a1b5186303abdc2b2e86b6d5eaad7f","tid":2238681,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac62a6eb61f6fb017f636ff5cc2f99b03a8a133","tid":2238681,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0